replies.body:
Hey, seems there's a bit of a misunderstanding.  That line is the joke from old Karthus.  Check under the history tab on old quotes -- http://leagueoflegends.wikia.com/wiki/Karthus  There's was no malicious intent with that comment.  

Saying that you can't wait for his account to get banned and that someone must be super toxic is 100% out of line and uncalled for.  Do not say these types of comments in the future and simply report anything you believe violates the rules.

{{sticker:poppy-wink}}
